00:45:00,764 --> 00:45:03,033
Mr. Kurokawa's childhood friend.

762
00:45:10,240 --> 00:45:13,410
His body build is very much
like Kurokawa's current one.

763
00:45:14,211 --> 00:45:15,312
CRIMINAL LAW JOURNAL

764
00:45:16,213 --> 00:45:19,850
I can't really remember this guy's face.

765
00:45:33,063 --> 00:45:35,999
THE DRAMA IS FICTITIOUS

766
00:45:36,600 --> 00:45:38,569
<i>It's the commonly-called</i>
<i>Oume Casanova Murder Case.</i>

767
00:45:38,635 --> 00:45:40,204
