768
00:45:40,270 --> 00:45:42,506
<i>As a lawyer, he is branded as a failure.</i>

769
00:45:42,573 --> 00:45:43,874
You should take off the badge.

770
00:45:43,941 --> 00:45:46,410
Maybe I'm not cut out to be a lawyer.

771
00:45:46,477 --> 00:45:49,446
