<i>an experiment to find out the truth.</i>

772
00:45:49,513 --> 00:45:51,014
<i>Mr. Kurokawa!</i>

773
00:45:51,081 --> 00:45:52,683
I'll investigate thoroughly…

774
00:45:52,750 --> 00:45:55,886
If you think you can't win,
I'll look for someone more skillful.

775
00:45:55,953 --> 00:45:56,820
His will?

776
00:45:56,887 --> 00:45:58,789
<i>She killed him for his money?</i>

777
00:45:58,856 --> 00:46:00,791
<i>I wonder what I'm trying to investigate.</i>

778
00:46:00,858 --> 00:46:03,660
Your life as a lawyer is really over.

779
00:46:03,727 --> 00:46:05,963
Marina, I want you to be saved!

